  "reference_number": "RUS1838",
  "remarks": "\nPJSC Severstal is an involved person under the Russia (EU Exit) (Sanctions) Regulations 2019 on the following grounds: \n(1) PJSC Severstal is and has been obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance, namely the Russian extractives sector and; (2) PJSC Severstal is owned or controlled directly or indirectly by a person involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia, namely Alexey MORDASHOV. \n",
